articles.title: Prior COVID-19 protects against subsequent infections - News-Medical.Net
articles.description: In a recent study published in the Journal of American Medical Association (JAMA), researchers evaluated the duration and level of protection conferred by a coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) infection among non-vaccinated subjects.
